You may wish to manually copy these to /root:

  /etc/skel/.bash_profile
  /etc/skel/.bashrc
  /etc/skel/.nanorc
  /etc/skel/.Xresources

I use Xfce, therefore the .xinitrc runs /usr/bin/startxfce4 by default.


Adding a normal user can be done by:

# useradd -m -s /bin/bash -c "Firstname Lastname" -g users -G disk,cdrom,audio,lp,video,wheel,scanner myuser
